channel.title: Hey guys, I'm Denis
channel.description:
Hi everyone,
I'm a full-time PHP developer working at a big multinational. I always get the urge of working at my own projects after hours though, giving me satisfaction I don't always get at my day job, I'm sure there are more of you like me. I'm really interested in reading more about of all your discussion here!
Cheers, Denis.
